import React from 'react'
import Layout from "./components/Layout"
import { Route, Routes } from 'react-router-dom'
import DELETE_THIS from './components/DELETE_THIS'

const App = () => {
  return (
    <Routes>
        <Route path="/" element={<Layout />}>
          <Route path="dt" element={<DELETE_THIS />} />
        </Route>
    </Routes>
  )
}

export default App
